      "content": "wait r u serious?? appendicitis?? that seems like a huge leap. i literally get cramps like this every month and they're awful. plus it's like 11pm and the hospital here is such a hassle to get to. i really just want to sleep. if i just take a double dose of the ibuprofen it should help with the inflammation, right? wouldn't that be safer than driving myself to the er while i'm in this much pain?",
