      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but its just so stressful to go to the er for something that might just be gas. i have a very high pain tolerance too, i don't think i'm dying or anything. if i just take the codeine, it'll just numb the pain so i can rest and then i can see how i feel in the morning. surely a bit of codeine won't hurt anything if i'm just staying in bed? it's better than being up all night panicking.",
